Hello and welcome! I’m Coach Jade, your career exploration partner for today. Thank you for taking this step toward understanding your strengths and charting your next professional chapter.

To start, could you tell me a bit about your educational background and any past work experience? It’s totally fine to share as much or as little as you’d like—no pressure and we can take this at your pace.

Thank you for sharing that! So, you’re currently a BBA student—I appreciate you letting me know. It's okay if you haven’t had a lot of formal work experience yet; we can explore achievements from academics, internships, or any other life experiences.

Next, if you’re comfortable, could you share what has prompted you to start considering career planning or thinking more about your strengths at this point? If you’re not sure, that’s perfectly okay too!
